articles.author: Lex Harvey, Catherine Nicholls
articles.title: French President Emmanuel Macron lands in Mayotte days after devastating cyclone - CNN
articles.description: French President Emmanuel Macron has met with residents of the Indian Ocean archipelago of Mayotte, days after the French overseas territory was hit by a devastating cyclone.
